== Icelandic ==

=== Etymology ===
From Old Norse, related to [[Norwegian]] ''englen''/''engel'', [[Swedish]] ''ängel'', [[Danish]] ''englen''/''engel''; and by extension [[Old English]] ''[[engel]]'', and [[German]] [[Engel]].

